quote_last: That meant I had been out for twenty minutes. Twenty minutes' sleep. Just a nice doze. In that time I had muffed a mob and lost eight thousand dollars.
quote_raw: The watch showed 10.56 p.m. That meant I had been out for twenty minutes. Twenty minutes' sleep. Just a nice doze. In that time I had muffed a mob and lost eight thousand dollars.
title: Farewell, My Lovely
author: Raymond Chandler

quote_last: . The stars were shining. The wind blew softly and carried the scent of decaying leaves and melting snow from the fields.
quote_raw: It was about eleven o'clock. The stars were shining. The wind blew softly and carried the scent of decaying leaves and melting snow from the fields.
title: The Hammer of God
author: Bo Giertz
